Author: NaturalZebra
Text: I’m a nurse too, and this is the stuff I honestly hate about it. Some are so catty and backstabbing, it’s like high school mean girls. It sucks :/ and who do you trust?

Author: CATrashanator
Text: I am honestly appalled that adults would even fucking do this. Who are these people? I tell myself that next time someone says anything about my weight, I’ll tell them to fuck off. But I’ll probably be so dumbfounded, that I won’t be able to speak.
